## SQL Techniques Used

- **CASE WHEN:** Conditional aggregation to segment employees by threshold
- **UNION ALL:** Combine multiple factor comparisons into single result set
- **GROUP BY:** Segment data across multiple dimensions (Department, JobLevel, etc.)
- **ROUND():** Format decimal places for readability
- **ORDER BY CASE:** Custom sorting (e.g., maintaining job level order instead of alphabetical)

