## Key Insights from SQL Analysis

1. **Work-Life Balance is the primary lever** (2.5-point satisfaction differential)
2. **98 employees are at-risk** (Stress >= 4 AND Satisfaction <= 2)
3. **IT and Finance departments are highest-risk** (23 and 21 at-risk respectively)
4. **41 Senior/Lead roles at-risk** (critical talent loss exposure)
5. **Overtime costs 0.42 satisfaction points** (affects 31% of workforce)
6. **Stress shows inverse relationship** with satisfaction (downward trend from level 1-5)

